; "Local pink fox enjoyer creates world's worst scripting language to split face sheets"
; delimited via tabs, tab width is 4 spaces (should already be configured for you thanks to .editorconfig)

; commands:
; BGN	sheet.png
;   opens a face sheet for splitting
; ADD	category	name	destination/path.png	(tag1,tag2...)
;   splits the face at the current index and advances the index by 1
;   tags are optional
; SKP	(count)
;   advances the index by count
;   count is optional, defaults to 1
;   count must be 1 or higher
; END
;   closes the currently open face sheet

; Melody
BGN	melody faces.png
ADD	Melody	Happy	melody/happy.png
ADD	Melody	Neutral	melody/neutral.png
ADD	Melody	Neutral, Looking to Side	melody/neutral_side.png
ADD	Melody	Sad	melody/sad.png
ADD	Melody	Happy, Looking to Side	melody/happy_side.png
ADD	Melody	Embarrassed	melody/embarrassed.png
ADD	Melody	Smug	melody/smug.png
ADD	Melody	Worried	melody/worried.png
ADD	Melody	Unamused	melody/unamused.png
ADD	Melody	Shocked	melody/shocked.png
ADD	Melody	Surprised	melody/surprised.png
ADD	Melody	Wistful	melody/oh_you.png
ADD	Melody	Flustered	melody/flustered.png
ADD	Melody	Furious	melody/fuckign_pissed.png
ADD	Melody	Angry	melody/pissed.png
ADD	Melody	Sad, Looking to Side	melody/sad_side.png
